title: The Time Tunnel - The Revenge Of Robin Hood Ep. 16
description: Doug and Tony are transported to England to the Thirteenth Century. There a group of barons, leaded by Baron Earl of Huntington (a.k.a. Robin Hood) are trying to force King John to sign the Magna Carta. The Earl of Huntington is captured and tortured in the dungeon in order to reveal the location of the meeting, while Doug and Tony organize with Friar Tuck, Little John and a group of outlaws to break in the castle and rescue Robin Hood.
